  "pages": [
    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "An interesting event of this week\nwill be the card party which will\nbe given next Tuesday afternoon\nby Mrs. Valentine Brasch and Mrs.\nw. G. Hall at the nome of the for\nmer at W719 Sixth avenue.\n\n\nThe affair is to be given for the\nbenefit of the Woman's club day\nnursery, and unusual interest is\nbeing shown by the charitable\nladies of the city. Arrangements\nwill be made to accommodate over\n100 guests."
    }
  ]
